dc_description_s: This data represents public land survey system (PLSS) corners for Langlade County, Wisconsin in 2021. [This information is collected by a certified Surveyor using a GPS system to mark each corner. Tie sheets are created for each one of those corners to help identify its unique location. These documents are being placed in various online formats. Maintenance and Update Frequency: Maintained by County Surveyor and / or Land Records Department Last Update: Dec 2020]
uw_supplemental_s: This is an archived copy of the data held at UW-Madison.
